{"tid":2023542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本空自宇宙作戰隊正式成立","createTime":"2020-05-19T05:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T05:54:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b45afae67d429ce0a7e4663d00d62097e675158f","tid":2023542,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.kyodonews.net/chinese/public/images/posts/27711e2f59a0bfea37fcb7a9dffc31c4/photo_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.kyodonews.net%2Fchinese%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fposts%2F27711e2f59a0bfea37fcb7a9dffc31c4%2Fphoto_l.jpg&h=ae5c51d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【共同社5月18日電】監視太空垃圾、隕石和可疑衛星以保護日本人造衛星的航空自衛隊&ldquo;宇宙作戰隊&rdquo;18日以府中基地（東京都府中市）為據點正式成立。這是首次設立專門從事太空監視的自衛隊部隊。防衛省將與美軍和日本宇宙航空研究開發機構（JAXA）合作，力爭構建情報共享系統。<br />\n<br />\n  美軍去年12月創建了1.6萬人規模的太空司令部，作為與陸海空並列的獨立軍。中國和俄羅斯據稱正在開發攻擊他國衛星的&ldquo;殺手衛星&rdquo;，日本也可能受到了太空軍事利用加速動向的影響。<br />\n<br />\n  18日在防衛省舉行的隊旗授予儀式上，防衛相河野太郎訓示稱，&ldquo;為了盡快適應新的安全保障環境，必須儘早構建太空情況監視等的體制&rdquo;。宇宙作戰隊隊長、二等空佐（相當於空軍中校）阿式俊英表示，&ldquo;首先重要的是人才培養，希望與美軍和JAXA合作&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n  據防衛省介紹，宇宙作戰隊啟動時編制約為20人。利用建在山口縣山陽小野田市的雷達監視高度約3.6萬公里的靜止軌道，執行保護人造衛星免受垃圾等威脅的任務，還力爭在2026年度前發射自己的太空監視衛星。<br />\n<br />\n  JAXA除靜止軌道外，還負責1000公里以下的低高度環繞軌道。自衛隊與JAXA、美軍共享情報的系統預定從2023年度開始運用。<br />\n<br />\n  自衛隊從2016年起每年參加美國戰略軍主辦的太空監視相關的多邊桌上演習。考慮向美國加利福尼亞州空軍基地內的太空作戰中心派遣聯絡官，推進加強部隊間的關係。（完）"},{"pid":"ed5beb68992e964d6a3b205b23d0d11b01cbf1fc","tid":2023542,"uid":40250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:44:03.000Z","msg":"係日本同美國上空都陪署反洲際導彈"},{"pid":"128f4f543fb3eb7af40ee7c6b349d3f28d5f4247","tid":2023542,"uid":55321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"幾時有高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f51e704864b1f9f680e9e0fdb1237f5ff39a04","tid":2023542,"uid":287392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"幾時有高達 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e1c62f8674a42135d10b4179be6fd21d1b4af1","tid":2023542,"uid":181088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7e60762f560d91c427a9012b83a7dc9459b769","tid":2023542,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"用衛星武器打爆北京"},{"pid":"6813969f79194939f08407a4eee893e0149c86e5","tid":2023542,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/414d8fa5ec5a7614cecdf30ff05310a5/tumblr_ox1wwu9PBM1wp4nx2o1_400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F414d8fa5ec5a7614cecdf30ff05310a5%2Ftumblr_ox1wwu9PBM1wp4nx2o1_400.jpg&h=439684fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"445c7b7829105f76991c35c90edfc1f67155c7d0","tid":2023542,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"美日聯合戰略太空司令部<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b63de5039573ab9b9a4a3dc5944c2e2ded2a1f2","tid":2023542,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.easyatm.com.tw/img/4/df9/nBnauM3XyMjN3ITNykjM3MjM2UTM1QDN5MjM5ADMwAjMwUzL5IzL3EzLt92YucmbvRWdo5Cd0FmLwE2LvoDc0RHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easyatm.com.tw%2Fimg%2F4%2Fdf9%2FnBnauM3XyMjN3ITNykjM3MjM2UTM1QDN5MjM5ADMwAjMwUzL5IzL3EzLt92YucmbvRWdo5Cd0FmLwE2LvoDc0RHa.jpg&h=1c94d8bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae744cbc7cfbc8457138ca32b5ee285411901b5a","tid":2023542,"uid":46323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"殖民衛星炮<img src=\"/assets/f